Success Nwogu, Abuja Former Vice-President, Atiku Abubakar, has said he has strong faith in God that Nigeria will defeat the coronavirus pandemic. He said this on his verified personal twitter handle @atiku, on Sunday. He expressed confidence that together, Nigerians would conquer COVID-19. Atiku said: “I wish all Nigerians, and Christians around the world, a happy Easter. “I have strong faith in God that Nigeria will rise and defeat this scourge, and together we will bid farewell to COVID-19 “However, we must not aim to return to normal. We must profit from our experiences, and return to better than normal. “We must return to increased patriotism, increased productivity, increased victory against our common challenges, and increased Unity and Faith, Peace and Progress.” Copyright PUNCH.
